Barclays Barred From Tokyo Stock Exchange Trading, Bourse Says

-- B y   J a s o n   C l e n f i e l d
-- 
2011-10-03T09:53:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/barclays-barred-from-tokyo-stock-exchange-trading-bourse-says.html
A Japanese unit of  Barclays Plc (BARC)  will
be barred from trading on the Tokyo Stock Exchange after it
failed to report some short sales to the exchange, the TSE said
today on its website.  Barclays Capital  will be suspended from trading from Oct.
11 to Oct. 24 on the bourse, according to the statement. The TSE
did not say what securities the brokerage may have shorted.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Clenfield in Tokyo at 
 jclenfield@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
